ed="T" n="0852a14"/><persName key="A012953">釋師簡</persName>，姓<name>趙</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000012388">丹丘</placeName>人也。弗循戒範，放肆<lb
ed="T" n="0852a15"/>恬然，擁破納衣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1322"/>，多誦詞偈，好懸記<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1165"/><placeName key="PL000000011518">杭</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000013265">越</placeName>間<lb
ed="T" n="0852a16"/>災福。初無信者，驗猶合符。於<persName key="A000008">一行</persName>、<persName key="A013851">景淳</persName>山<lb
ed="T" n="0852a17"/>經地理<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1811"/>別得徑門，常言：昔<placeName key="PL000000021580">泰山</placeName><persName key="A006977">道辯</persName>相塜得<lb
ed="T" n="0852a18"/>術，餘無取焉。喜為人遷山<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1854"/>相塚，吉凶如<lb
ed="T" n="0852a19"/>其言。居無定所，多遊族姓家，言腹飢，便求<lb
ed="T" n="0852a20"/>雞肉餐。此外得美酒，啜數杯而去。初無言<lb
ed="T" n="0852a21"/>謝，然長於勒書<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1855"/>──大字題牌、寺觀門額，書成<lb
ed="T" n="0852a22"/>相之，吉凶隨言，久近驗之。始居<placeName key="PL000000011593"><placeName>杭</placeName><placeName>西湖</placeName></placeName>旁<lb
ed="T" n="0852a23"/>院，無疾而終。後有行客自<placeName key="PL000000028663">長沙</placeName>市中見，携<lb
ed="T" n="0852a24"/>手話舊，寄言與<placeName key="PL000000011627">崇壽院</placeName>主：「汝先負錢若干，<lb
ed="T" n="0852a25"/>今放<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1406"/>汝。<ref type="person" target="#A012953">我</ref>眠床芻薦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1853"/>下層，有紙裹肉脯屑，<lb
ed="T" n="0852a26"/>必應腐敗，為棄之。」院僧依言，果然見之，因<lb
ed="T" n="0852a27"/>寫貌供養。<persName key="A012953">簡</persName>曾言「尖頭屋已後火化去。」及<lb
ed="T" n="0852a28"/>州南塔<date key="j20709902071373" notAfter-iso="+0959-02-15" notBefore-iso="+0958-01-28">戊午歲</date>被天火爇之<ptr target="#n2834"/>，應言無爽矣。</p>
